data.description: Live the good life in this spacious home in a beautiful neighborhood with desirable schools. The great floor plan has 5 bedrooms, 2 living areas, and a gorgeous kitchen. The kitchen has granite counters, a convection range, a breakfast bar, lots of cabinets and a full size pantry. Upstairs is a wide open loft that can be used for anything your heart desires. Beautiful luxury vinyl planks throughout all the main living spaces with brand new carpet in all the bedrooms. The primary bedroom is on the main floor, separate from all the other bedrooms, with an attached alcove perfect for a sitting area. The bathroom has a large soaking tub with separate shower. Using one central hub that talks to all the devices in your home, you can control the lights, thermostat and front door lock, all from your mobile device. There are so many perks, you need to see it to believe it! Call for your appt. today!
